text: FC Dinamo Tbilisi is a football club from Tbilisi, Georgia. The club was one of the best in the Soviet Top League, but after the Soviet Union broke up, the club joined the newly created league, the Umaglesi Liga. The team won the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup, Soviet Top League, Soviet Cup, Umaglesi Liga, Georgian Cup, Georgian Super Cup and the CIS Cup. == Honours == * UEFA Cup Winners' Cup: 1 1981 * Soviet Top League: 2 1964, 1978 * Soviet Cup: 2 1976, 1979 * Georgian League: 19 1990, 1991, 1992, 1993, 1994, 1995, 1996, 1997, 1998, 1999, 2003, 2005, 2008, 2013, 2014, 2016, 2019, 2020, 2022 * Georgian Cup: 13 1992, 1993, 1994, 1995, 1996, 1997, 2003, 2004, 2009, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016 * Georgian Super Cup: 9 1996, 1997, 1999, 2005, 2008, 2014, 2015, 2021, 2023 * CIS Cup winner: 1 2004 ==References== Category:European football clubs Category:Football in Georgia (country) Category:Tbilisi Category:1911 establishments Category:Sports organizations of Georgia (country)
